45     public ConfigurationBuilder() {
46        this.attributes = Configuration.attributeDefinitionSet();
47        this.clustering = new ClusteringConfigurationBuilder(this);
48        this.customInterceptors = new CustomInterceptorsConfigurationBuilder(this);
49        this.dataContainer = new DataContainerConfigurationBuilder(this);
50        this.deadlockDetection = new DeadlockDetectionConfigurationBuilder(this);
51        this.eviction = new EvictionConfigurationBuilder(this);
52        this.expiration = new ExpirationConfigurationBuilder(this);
53        this.indexing = new IndexingConfigurationBuilder(this);
54        this.invocationBatching = new InvocationBatchingConfigurationBuilder(this);
55        this.jmxStatistics = new JMXStatisticsConfigurationBuilder(this);
56        this.persistence = new PersistenceConfigurationBuilder(this);
57        this.locking = new LockingConfigurationBuilder(this);
58        this.security = new SecurityConfigurationBuilder(this);
59        this.storeAsBinary = new StoreAsBinaryConfigurationBuilder(this);
60        this.transaction = new TransactionConfigurationBuilder(this);
61        this.versioning = new VersioningConfigurationBuilder(this);
62        this.unsafe = new UnsafeConfigurationBuilder(this);
63        this.sites = new SitesConfigurationBuilder(this);
64        this.compatibility = new CompatibilityModeConfigurationBuilder(this);
65     }

174       return this;
175    }
176 
177    public <T extends Builder<?>> T addModule(Class<T> klass) {
178       try {
179          Constructor<T> constructor = klass.getDeclaredConstructor(ConfigurationBuilder.class);
180          T builder = constructor.newInstance(this);
181          this.modules.add(builder);
182          return builder;
183       } catch (Exception e) {
184          throw new CacheConfigurationException("Could not instantiate module configuration builder '" + klass.getName() + "'", e);
185       }
186    }
187 
188    @Override
189    public ConfigurationBuilder template(boolean template) {
190       this.template = template;
191       return this;
192    }
193 
194    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
195    public void validate() {
196       if (attributes.attribute(SIMPLE_CACHE).get()) {
197          validateSimpleCacheConfiguration();
198       }
199       for (Builder<?> validatable:
200             asList(clustering, customInterceptors, dataContainer, deadlockDetection, eviction, expiration, indexing,
201                    invocationBatching, jmxStatistics, persistence, locking, storeAsBinary, transaction,
202                    versioning, unsafe, sites, compatibility)) {
203          validatable.validate();
204       }
205       for (Builder<?> m : modules) {
206          m.validate();
207       }
208    }
209 
210    private void validateSimpleCacheConfiguration() {
211       if ((transaction.transactionMode() != null && transaction.transactionMode().isTransactional())
212             || !customInterceptors.create().interceptors().isEmpty()
213             || !persistence.stores().isEmpty()
214             || invocationBatching.isEnabled()
215             || indexing.enabled()
216             || storeAsBinary.create().enabled()
217             || compatibility.create().enabled()) {
218          throw log.notSupportedInSimpleCache();
219       }
220    }
221 
222    @Override
223    public void validate(GlobalConfiguration globalConfig) {
224       for (ConfigurationChildBuilder validatable:
225             asList(clustering, customInterceptors, dataContainer, deadlockDetection, eviction, expiration, indexing,
226                    invocationBatching, jmxStatistics, persistence, locking, storeAsBinary, transaction,
227                    versioning, unsafe, sites, compatibility)) {
228          validatable.validate(globalConfig);
229       }
230       // Modules cannot be checked with GlobalConfiguration
231    }
232 
233    @Override
234    public Configuration build() {
235       return build(true);
236    }
237 
238    public Configuration build(GlobalConfiguration globalConfiguration) {
239       validate(globalConfiguration);
240       return build(true);
241    }
242 
243    public Configuration build(boolean validate) {
244       if (validate) {
245          validate();
246       }
247       List<Object> modulesConfig = new LinkedList<Object>();
248       for (Builder<?> module : modules)
249          modulesConfig.add(module.create());
250       return new Configuration(template, attributes.protect(), clustering.create(), customInterceptors.create(),
251                dataContainer.create(), deadlockDetection.create(), eviction.create(),
252                expiration.create(), indexing.create(), invocationBatching.create(),
253                jmxStatistics.create(), persistence.create(), locking.create(), security.create(),
254                storeAsBinary.create(), transaction.create(), unsafe.create(), versioning.create(), sites.create(),
255                compatibility.create(),
256                modulesConfig);
257    }
258 
259    public ConfigurationBuilder read(Configuration template) {
260       this.attributes.read(template.attributes());
261       this.clustering.read(template.clustering());
262       this.customInterceptors.read(template.customInterceptors());
263       this.dataContainer.read(template.dataContainer());
264       this.deadlockDetection.read(template.deadlockDetection());
265       this.eviction.read(template.eviction());
266       this.expiration.read(template.expiration());
267       this.indexing.read(template.indexing());
268       this.invocationBatching.read(template.invocationBatching());
269       this.jmxStatistics.read(template.jmxStatistics());
270       this.persistence.read(template.persistence());
271       this.locking.read(template.locking());
272       this.security.read(template.security());
273       this.storeAsBinary.read(template.storeAsBinary());
274       this.transaction.read(template.transaction());
275       this.unsafe.read(template.unsafe());
276       this.sites.read(template.sites());
277       this.versioning.read(template.versioning());
278       this.compatibility.read(template.compatibility());
279 
280       for (Object c : template.modules().values()) {
281          Builder<Object> builder = this.addModule(ConfigurationUtils.builderFor(c));
282          builder.read(c);
283       }
284 
285       return this;
286    }
